39:15.562 --> 39:18.605
and I don't think any of us
will ever forget that.

39:19.482 --> 39:22.860
Once inside the zone,
the runners have three hours.

39:22.944 --> 39:25.821
They've got to go
through all four game quads.

39:25.905 --> 39:28.866
Three hours or less,
and they're going to need every second,

39:28.950 --> 39:31.034
'cause you know who's on their tail?

39:31.119 --> 39:33.036
The stalkers!

39:33.121 --> 39:35.873
- Who?
