40:00.148 --> 40:03.567
On your marks, get set...

40:03.902 --> 40:07.029
Killian, I'll be back.

40:10.825 --> 40:12.659
Only in a rerun.

40:13.745 --> 40:14.786
Go!

40:19.250 --> 40:21.752
- Go!
