43:09.545 --> 43:11.713
All right. Okay.

43:11.798 --> 43:16.510
We're looking for Subzero!

43:24.852 --> 43:27.687
And now, our first stalker of the evening,

43:27.772 --> 43:31.358
a Cadre trophy champion
with over 30 lifetime kills.

43:31.442 --> 43:33.735
Let's welcome the incredible ice-man

43:33.820 --> 43:38.198
