into quivering, bloody sushi,

43:38.282 --> 43:40.617
Professor Subzero!

44:01.681 --> 44:03.974
Move. Move it.

44:04.684 --> 44:06.351
Come on. Let's go!

44:28.082 --> 44:31.960
Damon, here in the locker room
there's a lot of excitement, here,

44:32.044 --> 44:33.462
